  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Metal comes with a comprehensive suite of advanced developer tools to help you debug and optimize your Metal apps.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Runtime-diagnostics",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Runtime diagnostics",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can enable API Validation when running your app to check for incorrect Metal API usage.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Validating-your-apps-Metal-API-usage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Enable Shader Validation when running your app to check for issues like out-of-bounds memory access, missing ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "useResource",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " calls, and stack overflows.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Validating-your-apps-Metal-shader-usage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The Metal Performance HUD offers a visual overlay to catch performance issues while your app is running.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Monitoring-your-Metal-apps-graphics-performance",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Runtime-performance-analysis",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Runtime performance analysis",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The Metal system trace tool in Instruments provides a visual timeline of the parallel work on the CPU and the GPU, and the memory usage of your Metal app.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "gputools-instruments-game-performance-hero.png",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can begin profiling with the Game Performance template (see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Analyzing-the-performance-of-your-Metal-app",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") or the Game Memory template (see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Analyzing-the-memory-usage-of-your-Metal-app",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ").",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Advanced-Metal-debugging-and-profiling",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Advanced Metal debugging and profiling",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The Metal debugger in Xcode provides advanced tools for debugging and profiling your Metal app.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "gputools-metal-debugger-hero.png",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can get summaries of your Metal workload with the Dependencies viewer and the Memory viewer, inspect individual resources, and selectively debug your shaders.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For more information on debugging, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Investigating-visual-artifacts",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In addition, you can optimize your Metal app by drilling down performance bottlenecks with the Performance timeline and the per-line shader profiling results.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For more information on profiling, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Optimizing-GPU-performance",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Learn more about ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/Metal-debugger",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
